androidx.percentlayout.widget

Interface PercentLayoutHelper.PercentLayoutParams

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PercentFrameLayout.LayoutParams, PercentRelativeLayout.LayoutParams
    Enclosing class:
    PercentLayoutHelper
    Deprecated. 
    this class is deprecated along with its parent class.

    @Deprecated
public static interface PercentLayoutHelper.PercentLayoutParams
    If a layout wants to support percentage based dimensions and use this helper class, its LayoutParams subclass must implement this interface. Your LayoutParams subclass should contain an instance of PercentLayoutInfo and the implementation of this interface should be a simple accessor.
